<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM1.7.10">
<l>akali lakalu maṇuki laṇukum</l>
<l>pukalu mariyaṉ poruvalla ṉemmā</l>
<l>ṉikari lavaṉpukaḻ pāṭi yiḷaippilam</l>
<l>pakalu miravum paṭintu kuṭaintē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>If one leaves he leaves. If one comes close he comes close.</l>
<l>He is difficult to enter, he is without equal, our lord.</l>
<l>Singing the praise of him who is matchless we are without fatigue,</l>
<l>day and night settling [and] toiling.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
